title: Reno on Record 2 - Plane Racing Interviews and Sounds
description:
Super rare CD with interviews and recording of vintage and modern aircraft. Only for true buffs old these old flyers and those who need some accurate sounds.

The air traffic to pilot squaks are the best.

The year of production is not on the CD or insert but this is clearly before the Internet was popular which places it early 90's or 80's.
